                    <h1>Directions</h1>
                <p><p><em><strong>From Highway 280</strong></em><strong> </strong>- take Foothill Expwy exit; south towards the hills for 5 miles on Foothill Blvd which becomes Stevens Canyon Rd when it crosses Stevens Creek Blvd and continues past Stevens Creek Reservoir and into Stevens Canyon; left fork at stop sign in Stevens Canyon onto Mt Eden Rd for 1.6 miles, left on Garrod Rd. About 15 minutes.</p>
<p><em><strong>From Highway 85</strong></em> - take De Anza Blvd exit; south towards Saratoga for 1 mile; right on Pierce Rd for 1.8 miles; right on Mt Eden Rd for 1 mile; right on Garrod Rd. About 10 minutes</p>
